eging online abuse and harassment,and Paris police have launched an investigation.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3323, \"end\": 3328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.323487263090478e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"harassment\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma is not, at this point, planning to take legal action over online harassment, and would prefer to focus on the many \\\"loving messages\\\" that have been pouring in.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3369, \"end\": 3375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.413702136177894e-12, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"legal action\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"the many \\\"loving messages\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performer been getting thousands of messages daily, she told The Associated Press, most of them positive but some that she described as \\\"violent\\\" and even \\\"from the Middle Ages.\\\"\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3605, \"end\": 3621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999961596586, \"rank\": 3