t people\", \"from\": 5457, \"to\": 5467}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 5469, \"to\": 5481}, {\"ngram\": \"trans\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5491}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5492, \"to\": 5498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been accused of trying to impose our vision on the world,\\\" Bardin said.\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our vision\", \"from\": 5544, \"to\": 5554}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5558, \"to\": 5567}, {\"ngram\": \"Bardin\", \"from\": 5570, \"to\": 5576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are not.\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"... We just want to let people know that we have a place in the world, and we are claiming that place.\\\"\", \"from\": 5596, \"to\": 5699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5626}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 5645, \"to\": 5652}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5665}, {\"ngram\": \"that place\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma spoke to the AP in a phone interview and later at her Paris workshop, a studio devoted to her drag performance.\", \"from\": 5701, \"to\": 5819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5701, \"end\": 5707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.413702136177894e-12, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 5721, \"end\": 5723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.11750361691514e-17, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 5762, \"end\": 5